{"tid":888605,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"顏射留證據！ 13年後惡狼終落網","createTime":"2018-11-04T01:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T02:11:47.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddac7faba3d4e374a66cf9aaf4463a9c8b630708","tid":888605,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T01:56:33.000Z","msg":"《聯合報》報導，台中市有毒品前科的易姓男子，2005年7月期間，在台中大雅區與一名國中少女攀談，少女騎單車離去後騎機車尾隨攔下，易男恐嚇少女「不要逼我發瘋、我要拿刀子出來」，隨後拉少女到附近草叢，意圖脫去少女長褲性侵，少女頑強抵抗，易男繼續恐嚇「信不信我在這裡就可以活活把妳打死」，隨後脫掉自己褲子，露出下體強行射精在少女臉上，少女事後到醫院驗傷。<br />\n<br />\n事隔13年，台中市豐原警分局今年間因易男另涉他案，比對DNA後發現後他就是13年前涉嫌強制猥褻的犯嫌，依法將全案函送偵辦；台中地院一審依強制猥褻罪，判易男3年10月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181104/1459937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181104%2F1459937&d=PA4%2BDzYEZCZIURZfFi40EMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=41fe38a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181104%2F1459937&h=3f894143\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181104/1459937</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae841bbd8633edfeefb494d8ad4d54d5b06ea13","tid":888605,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}